/* OSSO CHANGELOG */

/* Warning, this Changelog is not used anymore, sorry. */

2000-11-28 - Alessandro Iurlano
             Stefano Rosellini
             Added bootloader support for FAT12 and FAT16
             Adopted bcc as 16 bits C compiler for second stage kernel loader
             Create new disk creation option (make Disk-new) to use bcc code
	     Created doc directory

2000-11-13 - Alessandro Iurlano
	     Version 0.0.2 released
	     Changed C library into shared library
	     Added runtime support for shared library and ELF dynamic linking
	     Bug fixes

2000-08-23 - Alessandro Iurlano
	     Created CHANGELOG
	     Translated files in drivers/lib/include and
             drivers/lib/include/protocols


First version without changelog : Version 0.0.1-c